* [to_additive](https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/pull/17631/files#diff-a24fc4e713a823e86ff05256f10aa5ed0447d2fc2d28f1efc783fd36730be08fR51) is *not* ignored (new feature).

I also updated the PR description.

Let me know if you think that anything else is missing!

